{"tid":518320,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"用緊Logitech mx master mouse 既mac用家唔該入一入","createTime":"2018-01-03T08:06:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-27T10:13:01.000Z","uid":129940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8758cd449e11da5047f4a12019393ff16a0240cd","tid":518320,"uid":129940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T08:06:06.000Z","msg":"我本身用開g302再加bettertouchtool先用到MacBook 本身既gesture <br />\n<br />\n之前見隻mx master 2s有得玩gesture 仲做緊特價就買左<br />\n點知佢既gesture button 做唔到2 finger swipe <br />\n個Logitech option （用泥configure 隻mouse 既software)仲要唔可以同better touch tool 一齊用 最後要uninstall Logitech option 先去番同用gaming mouse 一樣既set up<br />\n<br />\n但用唔到Logitech option 就等於冇得較dpi, freescroll threahold 又冇得用佢自帶既gesture button <br />\n<br />\n有冇ching 都用緊mx master 同mac可以分享下<br />\n<br />\n好似有少1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e83b9b931dda7de1b2a103bede84c3d22b9c839b","tid":518320,"uid":53105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T09:53:06.000Z","msg":"一年保<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ccab64d84208804d6590d60a004cbceb1523ee9","tid":518320,"uid":129940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e83b9b931dda7de1b2a103bede84c3d22b9c839b","tid":518320,"uid":53105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T09:53:06.000Z","msg":"一年保<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T10:21:14.000Z","msg":"應該唔係壞 <br />\n<br />\n我覺得係high sierra 既問題<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打有同樣問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3240cbfb56ea3505a1f1b556bfbdaca246549afb","tid":518320,"uid":1123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T10:29:07.000Z","msg":"用緊anywhere <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  答你唔到"},{"pid":"6201f9f0c9d288714